"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-celebrity-news-1934197-gabby-logan-Olympics-heptathlon-complaint-katarina-johnson-thompson\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Gabby Loganhas made her feelings known about the nail-biting HeptathlonOlympicsevent on Friday August 9.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 104, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The sports presenter did not hold back when reacting to the lengthy event that has British Olympian Katarina Johnson-Thompson bidding for heptathlon gold on Day 14 at Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 106, \"to\": 284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 189, \"end\": 196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9952972227897167, \"rank\": 0.0033481268087732254, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 197, \"end\": 205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999996084625, \"rank\": 3.915595801729558e-10, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 206, \"end\": 231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Johnson-Thompson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katarina Johnson-Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Johnson-Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Johnson-Thompson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB star Katarina was Thursday night's leader in the seven-event heptathlon and hopes to end her long wait for a Games medal by this evening when things wrap up.\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 451, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 286, \"end\": 293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.085788522120793e-14, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 299, \"end\": 307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Waters\", \"score\": 0.9999999519259302, \"rank\": 4.617351847194378e-08, \"text\": \"Katarina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Waters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Waters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it has been all too much for Gabby as she has taken in all the action.\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 527, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When fellow broadcaster and Olympian Jeanette Kwayke took to X to ask: \\\"Anyone else feeling SICK watching this heptathlon Long Jump?\\\"\", \"from\": 528, \"to\": 661, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 556, \"end\": 564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999996084625, \"rank\": 3.915595801729558e-10, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 565, \"end\": 573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeanette_Biedermann\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.182762079348141e-14, \"text\": \"Jeanette\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeanette_Biedermann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeanette_Biedermann\"}, {\"begin\": 650, \"end\": 659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Long_jump\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1566638019539306e-45, \"text\": \"Long Jump\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Long_jump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Long_jump\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gabby, 51, concurred by responding with a vomiting emoji.\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Whike Katarina's long jump was a triumph, keeping her in first place, the javelin match eclipsed her achievements soon after.\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 846, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE:Olympic gold medallist responds after BBC's Gabby Logan brands athlete 'selfish'  Katarina's main gold-medal rival Nafi Thiam opened the javelin competition in epic form with an effort of 54.04metres, a season's best which puts her 121 points past the Team GB star in the javelin.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 1140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 898, \"end\": 901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.8527471896084825, \"rank\": 0.1580159659901065, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 904, \"end\": 915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabby_Logan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gabby Logan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabby_Logan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabby_Logan\"}, {\"begin\": 975, \"end\": 979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafi_language\", \"score\": 0.9382360940984357, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nafi\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafi_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafi_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1112, \"end\": 1119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.085788522120793e-14, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is a significant lead going into tonight's concluding 800m race, which is likely to have Gabby remain on edge.\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1257, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not the first time Logan has made her feelings known about this year's games.She recently cast doubt over the winner's bell at the Paris 2024 Olympics, a revered tradition in athletics events.\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1283, \"end\": 1288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_River\", \"score\": 0.9751517721373956, \"rank\": 0.0254769254865574, \"text\": \"Logan\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Logan_River\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bell is typically rung by winners of events, however, Gabby spotted a potential issue with the timing of the bell during the celebrations.\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"?\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1603, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"?????\", \"from\": 1603, \"to\": 1608, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Naga Munchetty's BBC radio show sparks frenzy with awkward Olympics blunder  Do not miss:Meghan Markle fans all say the same thing after spotting odd gesture at Harry  Do not miss:Princess Anne's \\u00a36.8m home that was incredible gift from the late Queen  The incident occurred when Sweden's pole-vaulting champion Armand Duplantis triumphantly rang the bell after securing his gold medal.\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 2008, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1622, \"end\": 1636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Naga_Munchetty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Naga Munchetty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Naga_Munchetty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Naga_Munchetty\"}, {\"begin\": 1639, \"end\": 1642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.8527471896084825, \"rank\": 0.1580159659901065, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 1711, \"end\": 1724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meghan,_Duchess_of_Sussex\", \"score\": 0.9999999986252988, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Meghan Markle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meghan,_Duchess_of_Sussex\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meghan,_Duchess_of_Sussex\"}, {\"begin\": 1902, \"end\": 1908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"score\": 0.9999986446887396, \"rank\": 1.25179600767479e-06, \"text\": \"Sweden\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\"}, {\"begin\": 1934, \"end\": 1950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Armand Duplantis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sharing her scepticism, Gabby said: \\\"Now, I have noticed this, that the bell starts to ring before the timer actually calls the bell.\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2143, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am hoping, I am not seeing..\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2174, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's like Santa Claus.\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2185, \"end\": 2196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Claus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.282847155791877e-16, \"text\": \"Santa Claus\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Claus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santa_Claus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Is that what I am seeing?\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2223, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Is this a bit of theatre going on down there?\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2269, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\", she asked.\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2282, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She added firmly: \\\"In the name of good journalism I want to make sure that that bell is real.\\\"\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2378, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It came afterGabby bravely opened up about her personal health struggles.\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2453, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Welsh star revealed she was having memory troubles, which led to her hesitating on-air and proved particularly challenging while covering major events like the Olympics for theBBC.\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2638, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2640, \"to\": 2749, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2826, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2827, \"to\": 2859, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy    The \\\"brain fog\\\" Gabby experienced is a well-documented symptom of perimenopause, often described by women as feeling like their heads are full of \\\"cotton wool\\\".\", \"from\": 2860, \"to\": 3046, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the former rhythmic gymnast found solace in identifying the cause of her forgetfulness.\", \"from\": 3048, \"to\": 3144, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To help combat this, she adopted the method of keeping a piece of paper with her on-set to quickly note down names.\", \"from\": 3145, \"to\": 3260, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was always so good at recall,\\\" she told The Telegraph.\", \"from\": 3262, \"to\": 3319, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I got through a law degree basically just by going, 'Ah, page 32, Smith versus Cook'.\", \"from\": 3320, \"to\": 3406, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was always good with names, finding the right word at the right time, and I'd find myself humming a bit or using 'very, very, very'.\", \"from\": 3407, \"to\": 3541, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She added: \\\"Then, when I realised it was a symptom of perimenopause, it was actually a relief, like it normally is when you realise something is part of a process and you can do something about it.\\\"\", \"from\": 3543, \"to\": 3741, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3743, \"to\": 3912, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3880, \"end\": 3893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.024758409446419e-29, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3914, \"to\": 3981, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3929, \"end\": 3942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.024758409446419e-29, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"